@vinothchandar In my project that I'm working on, data from source has added a col named `extend_deal_type`. It has 3 types: 1 -> add, 2 -> update, 3 -> delete. I referred `TestRawTripPayload ` and then changed some codes in `OverwriteWithLatestAvroPayload.java`.
```
  @Override
  public Optional<IndexedRecord> getInsertValue(Schema schema) throws IOException {
    GenericRecord baseRecord = HoodieAvroUtils.bytesToAvro(recordBytes, Schema.parse(schemaStr));
    Object dealType = baseRecord.get("extend_deal_type");
    if (dealType != null && "3".equals(String.valueOf(dealType))) {
      return Optional.empty();
    }
    return Optional.of(HoodieAvroUtils.rewriteRecord(baseRecord, schema));
  }
```
